          "description": "I had a cough that would not go away. My primary care physician was on vacation so I thought of Urgent Care because it is close by and 2 people I knew had been there. I read the reviews and was not sure because reviews were rather bad about Dr Chen and about their billing.\nI went anyway and they could not have been nicer or more efficient. I was given a flu and Covid test as well as a chest X-ray because of my mature age. I asked about the billing because I was wary from what I read and everything was explained to me.\nI am very impressed with Dr Chen and his staff. We are very lucky to have them in our neighborhood. I highly recommend them.",
