          "description": "My wife waited over two hours for an X-ray after being told they would be able to take us quickly because we had a referral from another city md location.  We were \"next in line\" for over an hour until they took someone else for an X-ray in front of us.  We ended up leaving and not getting anything done because we had another appointment we had to make.  Incredibly frustrating and disappointing.  Only go here if it's your last resort or you enjoy spending your entire day in a waiting room.",
