          "description": "The whole point of coming here was to get a TB test. Was asked for insurance but was told insurance doesn\u2019t cover this and had to pay 225. When I showed up to get it read I made an appointment and was told that I would still have to wait over an hour. This didn\u2019t make sense because other individuals with later appointments or no appointments at all, that showed up after me were seen before me. I find it absolutely ridiculous with the systems that are in place in this establishment.",
