          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKBf28ffdmhOM8bqb8FRS_oq5mDeooZi_WgzhVB0Zq4HL3ZKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "For the sake of god. I made appointment at 4.30 and it\u2019s 5pm now. Still waiting. And there is no patients here besides me and another gentleman. What the hell happened to this city MD . It never used to be like this. Completely unacceptable. Do not come to this location. One of the receptionist was nice though.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GNFh6VldjbEpKVUZaZmQySldVblpNZHpGVmRYYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xc40604440bd5b029!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmF4XzVWclJJUFZfd2JWUnZMdzFVdXc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "3 months ago",
